57 the United Methodist Church; and
58 WHEREAS, through her work, Cathy has passionately
59 demonstrated a lifelong commitment to service, leadership,
60 and the advancement of educational and community
61 initiatives; now therefore,
62 BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES OF THE
63 LEGISLATURE OF ALABAMA, That we hereby most highly commend
64 Cathy Mitchell for faithful devotion to her community as an
65 educator at the IMPACT Learning Center, and we extend to her
66 our heartfelt gratitude and sincere best wishes for
67 continued health, happiness, and fulfillment in her future
68 endeavors.
